            "134360071/e 134360041/F/f Emet-Selch 1750/t 900 1700/c 1": "none/42 16/Emet-Selch 42 15 1 farmer 41 18 0 Abigail 40 23 0/skippable/move Abigail 0 -9 0 true/pause 1000/faceDirection Emet-Selch 3/pause 1100/speak Emet-Selch \"I noticed you're carrying a sword and not much else.$0#$b#Do you plan on a full expedition on such limited supply?$u\"/pause 400/faceDirection Abigail 1/pause 300/speak Abigail \"Yeah, I do. The risk is worth the gems.$3\"/pause 300/speak Emet-Selch \"Is that so?$h\"/pause 500/speak Abigail \"If you're going to say adventuring is too dangerous for me, save it.$a\"/pause 300/speak Emet-Selch \"Hmm. Struck a nerve, did I?$u\"/pause 200/speak Abigail \"...Just get lost.$a\"/pause 100/speak Emet-Selch \"Save your glowering, I'm not going to waste my time trying to convince you otherwise. I can see you've made up your mind.\"/pause 300/speak Abigail \"Great. Bye.$a\"/pause 500/faceDirection Abigail 0/pause 700/move Abigail 0 -1 0/speak Emet-Selch \"I said I wasn't going to convince you, not that I had nothing to say.\"/pause 400/faceDirection Abigail 2/speak Abigail \"Whatever it is, I'm not interested.$3\"/pause 200/faceDirection Emet-Selch 0/speak Emet-Selch \"If you bothered to listen, you'd know this is in your best interest.$7\"/pause 200/move farmer 0 -1 0/pause 100/emote farmer 28/pause 1000/faceDirection Emet-Selch 2/pause 500/speak Emet-Selch \"...Alright, alright.$7\"/pause 300/facedirection Emet-Selch 3/pause 300/speak Emet-Selch \"I have something to give to you.\"/pause 500/faceDirection Abigail 2/pause 200/emote Abigail 8/pause 500/speak Emet-Selch \"I do sincerely hope your adventure goes well.$0#$b#But in the event that it doesn't, take this with you.$0\"/pause 1000/faceDirection Emet-Selch 2/showFrame Emet-Selch 16/pause 100/showFrame Emet-Selch 17/pause 100/showFrame Emet-Selch 18/pause 100/showFrame Emet-Selch 19/pause 1200/showFrame Emet-Selch 20/pause 100/playSound skeletonStep/showFrame Emet-Selch 21/playSound wand/addObject 40 15 773 1/pause 100/showFrame Emet-Selch 22/pause 300/showFrame Emet-Selch 23/pause 1000/showFrame Emet-Selch 18/pause 100/showFrame Emet-Selch 17/pause 100/showFrame Emet-Selch 16/pause 100/showFrame Emet-Selch 0/pause 800/faceDirection Emet-Selch 3/pause 100/move Abigail 0 1 2/pause 300/playSound pickUpItem/removeObject 40 15/pause 200/speak Abigail \"Some medicine?$6#$b#Oh that's... actually really nice.$6#$b#Thanks.$0\"/pause 400/move Abigail 0 -7 0 true/pause 1500/faceDirection Emet-Selch 2/pause 300/playSound pickUpItem/speak Emet-Selch \"Here. You may take one as well.[773]\"/pause 800/speak Emet-Selch \"I meant my warning from our first encounter in the mines, you know. Do be careful.$0#$b#I've laid enough souls to rest.$6\"/pause 2000/end"
