      //Emet eight-heart event: history class is in the mines today. I hope you like au lore
      //Conditions: mines, 6am - 9pm, six-heart event, seven-heart event, eight hearts
      //also sends mail about hey please wait for story to play out before getting hitched (and mail for next emet fetch quest)
      {
        "Action": "EditData",
        "Target": "Data/Events/Mine",
        "Entries": {
            "134360081/e 134360061/e 134360071/f Emet-Selch 2000/t 600 2100": "none/18 7/Emet-Selch 18 6 2 farmer 18 13 0/mail 13436_Emet_8hearts/mail 13436_Emet_quartz/skippable/faceDirection Emet-Selch 0/move farmer 0 -4 0/pause 500/faceDirection Emet-Selch 2/pause 300/speak Emet-Selch \"Oh, hello, @.$h#$b#I was about to survey the deeper areas of the mines. Would you care to accompany me?$h#$b#I could teach you a thing or two.$u\"/pause 500/emote farmer 32/pause 1000/speak Emet-Selch \"Excellent.$u\"/pause 500/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000 true/playSound stairsdown/pause 500/changeLocation Custom_EmetSelchCustomNPC_Mine/viewport 14 12 true/warp Emet-Selch 16 11/warp farmer 15 13/globalFadeToClear/pause 500/move Emet-Selch 3 0 1/pause 1000/move Emet-Selch -6 0 3/pause 1000/move Emet-Selch 3 0 1/pause 1000/speak Emet-Selch \"The aether here is still considerably thinned. But where before the Underworld was unaffected, it too has grown weaker.\"/pause 400/emote farmer 8/pause 600/faceDirection Emet-Selch 2/pause 100/speak Emet-Selch \"The Underworld, the aetherial sea.\"/pause 700/speak Emet-Selch \"Do they not even teach you that much? I thought the Aetherial Sea was the more modern term, not that the basic concept itself was lost to time.$6\"/pause 500/speak Emet-Selch \"Very well. As the term describes, it is a sea of aetheric energy, composed of the souls of those not currently living.$0#$b#It is where your soul returns upon death, and from whence it springs forth to live its next life.\"/pause 300/speak Emet-Selch \"Its currents flow through all the world, but its true domain is within its heart. The ever-flowing aetherial sea blends with the physical realm as you go deeper.#$b#Thus, such caverns are subject to its currents, their depths ever shifting and changing as a result.#$b#The strong influence of the Underworld makes them ideal locations to observe its flow, as I am now.\"/pause 600/faceDirection Emet-Selch 1/pause 400/faceDirection Emet-Selch 3/pause 500/speak Emet-Selch \"The weakening of the physical realm, followed by the Underworld...$8\"/pause 200/speak Emet-Selch \"...Aether must be coalescing somewhere in physical form. First draining the environs, leaving little to replenish the aetherial sea.$9\"/pause 300/faceDirection Emet-Selch 2/pause 300/textAboveHead \"*sigh*\"/pause 700/speak Emet-Selch \"Would that you could spot it.$6#$b#But thank you, it has been a long time since I've done such a survey with another.$n#$b#I'd forgotten the presence of company while working can be... pleasant.$h#$b#Though you're a far better audience than *some* I could name.\"/pause 300/emote farmer 8/pause 1000/faceDirection Emet-Selch 0/pause 300/speak Emet-Selch \"Once, I would embark on these forays in a party of three.$h#$b#They weren't part of my duty, back then. Just adventures for their own sake, or in search of something or other we were tasked with finding.$h#$b#That was before I-or rather, we-joined the Convocation.\"/pause 300 /speak Emet-Selch \"Few know of it now, but ages ago, it was known to all as the foremost authority in all aspects of life.#$b#Fourteen chosen for their expertise and skills, to act as a steady guiding hand. To that end, its members are bestowed with a powerful enchantment--immortality.\"/pause 200/speak Emet-Selch \"I was chosen for the seat of Emet-Selch for my ability to see aether. Emet-Selch's domain is the balance thereof, between the physical realm and the aetherial sea.\"/pause 300/speak Emet-Selch \"Though I was not the first choice.$9#$b# That honor belonged to a friend, but he turned it down. Claimed I was better suited for the work.$9#$b#And so I've carried the responsibility since, alongside our third; they took the seat of Azem, the traveler.$n\"/pause 200/faceDirection Emet-Selch 2/pause 200/speak Emet-Selch \"It may no longer be so renowned in this era, or  known at all to many. But the Convocation remains, ascending new members as necessary, lending its aid when needed.$n#$b#Such as now, with this conundrum.$6\"/pause 600/speak Emet-Selch \"But I've seen enough for now, and I'm sure you've had your fill of my reminiscing.$9#$b#I enjoyed the change of pace, @.$h\"/move Emet-Selch -2 0 3/pause 1000/end"
        }
      },

