ySound yoba/pause 100/showFrame farmer 5/pause 200/temporarySprite 11 12 3 8 50 false 1/pause 50/playSound yoba/playsound coldSpell/pause 300/temporarySprite 8 11 3 8 50 false 1/pause 50/playSound yoba/pause 100/temporarySprite 15 12 3 8 50 false 1/pause 50/playSound yoba/pause 500/temporarySprite 8 11 3 8 50 false 1/pause 50/playSound yoba/pause 300/temporarySprite 11 14 3 8 50 false 1/pause 50/pause 500/stopGlowing/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000 true/pause 1000/playSound stairsdown/pause 1400/playSound stoneStep/pause 350/playSound stoneStep/pause 350/playSound stoneStep/pause 500/speak Emet-Selch \"Now how does the Underworld fare today...$8\"/pause 500/speak Emet-Selch \"...@? @!$11\"/pause 250/playSound stoneStep/pause 250/playSound stoneStep/pause 250/playSound stoneStep/pause 2500/playSound skeletonStep/pause 500/playSound wand/changeLocation Custom_EmetSelchCustomNPC_House/warp farmer 18 7/warp Emet-Selch 15 7/faceDirection Emet-Selch 2/faceDirection farmer 2/eyes 1 -10000/viewport 18 8 true/globalFadeToClear 0.005 continue/pause 1000/move Emet-Selch 0 3 2/pause 1000/move Emet-Selch 0 -3 0/pause 500/eyes 4 -10000/pause 200/faceDirection Emet-Selch 1/pause 200/emote Emet-Selch 16/pause 900/move Emet-Selch 1 0 1/pause 500/speak Emet-Selch \"Finally, you decide to wake.$6#$b#How are you feeling?\"/quickQuestion How are you?#Not great.#I could be better, but I think I'll be okay now.#Not bad, considering I passed out!(break)speak Emet-Selch \"Yes, I would imagine so.$0\"(break)speak Emet-Selch \"...About the best you could hope for, considering what you went through.$0\"(break)speak Emet-Selch \"Do you have any idea-!$6#$b#...$9\"/pause 300/faceDirection Emet-Selch 2/pause 200/speak Emet-Selch \"It would appear concentrations of aether in portions of the mine have become so low, crystals within the rock draw in any that comes near.$0\"/pause 200/faceDirection Emet-Selch 1/pause 200/speak Emet-Selch \"In this case, yours. I found you on the cavern floor, near-drained of aether.$6\"/pause 300/speak Emet-Selch \"If I hadn't chanced to find you...$0#$b#You would not have survived.$6\"/pause 400/faceDirection Emet-Selch 2/pause 700/speak Emet-Selch \"Have I not told you I've laid enough reckless souls to rest..!!$2\"/pause 300/faceDirection Emet-Selch 1/pause 100/move farmer -1 0 3/pause 300/emote farmer 20/pause 500/move Emet-Selch -1 0 1/speak Emet-Selch \"...$2\"/pause 800/faceDirection Emet-Selch 2/pause 800/speak Emet-Selch \"...$9\"/pause 200/speak Emet-Selch \"I've replenished your aether with my own, but you're like to feel weak for a time.$0#$b#Rest for the night, will you.$9\"/pause 300/move Emet-Selch 0 2 2/pause 600/speak Emet-Selch \"I will continue my search for the cause of such dramatic fluctuations.#$b#Do not count on your luck to see you through further forays. It will not last indefinitely.$6\"/pause 900/advancedMove Emet-Selch false 0 1 -3 0 0 -5/end newDay"
