      //Emet ten-hearts (PART ONE): local man grieves polycule
      //Conditions: his house, ten am - two am, nine-heart event, ten hearts
      //SPECIAL: starts 13436_EmetDrama dialogue topic for following 7B days, after which part two event can happen.

      {
        "Action": "EditData",
        "Target": "Data/Events/Custom_EmetSelchCustomNPC_House",
        "Entries": {
            "134360101/e 134360091/F /f Emet-Selch 2500/t 800 2600": "none/8 8/farmer 10 14 3 Emet-Selch 7 9 0/addConversationTopic 13436_EmetDrama 7/skippable/move farmer -3 0 3/move farmer 0 -3 0/pause 500/faceDirection Emet-Selch 2/pause 500/showFrame Emet-Selch 29/pause 800/textAboveHead Emet-Selch \"...\"/pause 900/speak Emet-Selch \"...What game are you playing here, @? What is it you wish of me?$0\"/pause 600/emote farmer 20/pause 1200/speak Emet-Selch \"...$s\"/pause 200/speak Emet-Selch \"...I see.$0\"/pause 400/faceDirection Emet-Selch 2/pause 500/speak Emet-Selch \"Tell me, do you recall what I agreed to, when you presented me with the bouquet?\"/pause 500/speak Emet-Selch \"A dalliance. An enjoyable distraction, if you will.$6#$b#A far cry from what you seem to think this is.\"/pause 800/speak Emet-Selch \"So allow me to leave no room for doubt. I have had loves, in the past.$n#$b#And I have no need for another.$6\"/pause 600/speak Emet-Selch \"Yet *you* would have me uncertain, and dare me to believe otherwise.$10#$b#Do you honestly think you can make me happy?$5\"/pause 700/move Emet-Selch 0 -1 0/pause 500/faceDirection Emet-Selch 2/pause 300/speak Emet-Selch \"I was happy, for a time. And do you know what becomes of such happiness?$10\"/pause 300/speak Emet-Selch \"Azem and I were ascended to the Convocation, with all the gifts that endows.$9#$b#But life did not stop for our third, Hythlodaeus, and eventually the truth of time became impossible to ignore.$9\"/pause 200/speak Emet-Selch \"Oh, I tried to thwart it. By artifact, by magick--any possible path one could imagine.$10\"/pause 200/speak Emet-Selch \"I all but begged him to accept the seat he had rejected and become Emet-Selch in my place, so at least he could live on.$9\"/pause 400/speak Emet-Selch \"And the stubborn fool refused it until the end.$s#$b# *Insisted* that I could do so much more for the world than he, that he would gladly accept his passing if it meant such would come to fruition.$s\"/pause 400/speak Emet-Selch \"So I lived. And he died.$9\"/pause 700/speak Emet-Selch \"Not that the seat alone could have guaranteed his remaining by our side, no.$10\"/pause 200/speak Emet-Selch \"Azem, too, had the powers granted by the Convocation. We remained, lifespans lengthened indefinitely, until titles relinquished.$n#$b#But they were never content to simply sit idle as time carried on.$6\"/pause 300/speak Emet-Selch \"Ever thrusting themselves into greater and greater dangers for the sake of others, they continued their duties, heedless of my warnings.$9#$b#In my fear, I bade them to call upon me should circumstances turn dire.$s#$b#And at times they did, and I would render aid.$n#$b#I even believed it would be enough to bring them home.$9\"/pause 200/speak Emet-Selch \"Until it wasn't.$s\"/pause 600/faceDirection Emet-Selch 0/pause 700/speak Emet-Selch \"If there is aught I know to be true, it is this: no force in this world is enough to keep you by my side, or bring back what was lost.$s\"/pause 200/faceDirection Emet-Selch 2/pause 200/speak Emet-Selch \"So I suggest you deliberate, alone, until that is understood.$10\"/quickQuestion I suggest you deliberate, alone, until that is understood.#I don't want to do that, and I don't think you do either.#...I see.#You're wrong, I wasn't interested in anything permanent.(break)speak Emet-Selch \"...Perhaps. But I will not suffer such again.$9\"(break)speak Emet-Selch \"...I'm sorry, @. But it is best I make myself clear here and now.$s\"(break)speak Emet-Selch \"...$11#$b#Excellent. I'm simply ensuring you know how little I require from you.$u\"/pause 300/speak Emet-Selch \"Now, it is best you go.$n\"/pause 2000/end invisible Emet-Selch"
        }
      },

