rdswipe/jump Beaft 8/pause 50/screenFlash 1/playSound flameSpell/pause 1000/speak Emet-Selch \"Enough of this.$12#$b#Away with you!$13\"/pause 400/stopAnimation Emet-Selch-Transformed 9/pause 1000/playSound powerup/screenFlash 3/playSound serpentDie/warp Beaft -100 -100/addTemporaryActor Rift 32 32 11 10 2 false/showFrame Rift 0/stopMusic/pause 300/showFrame Rift 1/pause 400/showFrame Rift 2/pause 400/animate Rift false true 400 2 3/stopJittering/pause 1200/showFrame Emet-Selch-Transformed 0/pause 500/animate Emet-Selch-Transformed false true 100 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7/pause 3000/stopGlowing/playMusic winter1/pause 2500/speak Emet-Selch \"Are you hurt?$12\"/pause 100/faceDirection farmer 0/pause 300/move farmer 3 0 0/pause 400/emote farmer 32/pause 1500/faceDirection farmer 1/move farmer 2 0 0/pause 100/emote farmer 8/pause 1000/speak Emet-Selch \"That was a departed soul, trapped in this realm.$12#$b# And the cause of my recent woes besides.$13#$b#It had to have drawn in massive quantities of aether to regain form as it did.$12\"/pause 600/speak Emet-Selch \"I opened a passage to the aetherial sea and bid it return; The rift will close soon enough.$12\"/pause 200/speak Emet-Selch \"Though I'm certain there was a pull from the other side as well...$13\"/pause 2000/textAboveHead Rift \"Oh! It's holding!\"/pause 50/playSound dwoop/jump Emet-Selch-Transformed 8/pause 10/emote farmer 16/pause 100/pause 1800/stopAnimation Rift 3/pause 400/showFrame Rift 4/pause 400/showFrame Rift 5/pause 400/animate Rift false true 400 6 7/pause 1000/speak Soulseer \"Theeeereee we are.$0\"/pause 50/pause 200/speak Soulseer \"An excellent show as always, my friend.$0#$b#And what a treat to see you in full form!$3\"/pause 200/speak Emet-Selch \"-Hythlodaeus! You're-$14\"/speak Soulseer \"Taking my time in the Underworld?$0#$b# Well of course. We can hardly go on to the next life without our dear Hades!$3\"/pause 1000/warp Emet-Selch-Transformed -200 -200/showFrame Emet-Selch 24/warp Emet-Selch 9 9/animate Emet-Selch false false 100 25 26 25 25 26 27 27 0/playSound wand/pause 1000/move Emet-Selch 0 2 1/pause 300/move Emet-Selch 1 0 1/pause 300/speak Emet-Selch \"You're still...$2\"/speak Soulseer \"Don't get the wrong idea, now. Azem and I are quite content to wait as long as we must.#$b#We wouldn't dream of keeping the most eminent Emet-Selch from his duties!$3\"/speak Emet-Selch \"Really, because I recall otherwi-$6\"/speak Soulseer \"Nonsense!$3#$b#But I do admit...#$b#I have some concerns to voice.$0\"/pause 400/stopAnimation Rift 8/pause 400/animate Rift false true 400 9 8/speak Emet-Selch \"Concerns?$0\"/pause 200/speak Soulseer \"For you, love.$1#$b#I do try and see how you fare, when such glimpses are afforded to me.$1\"/pause 300/speak Soulseer \"To see you hurt, watch you refuse yourself any happiness... it's terrible.$1#$b#You've been left alone for so long, and for that I am sorry.$1\"/pause 400/speak Soulseer \"But please, don't let that be reason to deny life's joys, fleeting though they may be.$1\"/pause 100/speak Soulseer \"Such wonderful things will pass, yes.$1#$b#But that is true regardless of if they are experienced... or forsaken.$1\"/pause 400/speak Soulseer \"And given the choice... I would much rather see you embrace them.$0\"/pause 400/speak Soulseer \"So please, go and live a little. Share your life, and your love!$3#$b#You do have someone waiting to share their own with you, after all.$2\"/pause 1000/speak Soulseer \"With that, I suppose I should get going. It was lovely meeting you, @.$0#$b#Do take care of our Emet-Selch, would you?$3\"/speak Emet-Selch \"Hythlodaeus!$11\"/speak Soulseer \"Now now, I said I wouldn't interfere with your good work.#$b#Just as well, for there is a newly-arrived 'errant soul' here that could use a touch of help.#$b#I may not carry a title, but surely that is just as worthy a cause to attend to?\"/pause 300/faceDirection Emet-Selch 2/pause 100/textAboveHead Emet-Selch \"...\"/pause 2000/textAboveHead Emet-Selch \"*sigh*\"/pause 2000/faceDirection Emet-Selch 1/pause 200/speak Emet-Selch \"Of course the one time I wish you *would* interrupt my day with chatter is the one time you find your own work to do.$1\"/speak Soulseer \"You wish for my 'chatter', do you? I shall have to remember that when next you claim otherwise.$2#$b#After all...with a flow of so much aether, I suspect the path between realms may persist for a time. But I digress.$0\"/pause 200/speak Soulseer \"Until next we meet.$0\"/playSound dwop/jump Emet-Selch 3/speak Emet-Selch \"Of course I wish-$2\"/pause 200/speak Emet-Selch \"...$9#$b#Until next we meet.$1\"/pause 2000/stopAnimation Rift 1/pause 500/playSound powerup/showFrame Rift 0/pause 500/warp Rift -150 -150/pause 1500/faceDirection Emet-Selch 2/pause 900/speak Emet-Selch \"@.$0#$b#Go home and rest.$0#$b#I'll disperse any remaining aether.$9\"/pause 1500/move farmer -10 0 3 true/pause 2000/end invisible Emet-Selch"
